# AIGlass Backend API

![Build Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/build-passing-brightgreen)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue)
![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-informational)

The AIGlass Backend is the official RESTful API that powers the AI Smart Glass. It handles user authentication, data processing, and core business logic, providing a secure and scalable foundation for the smart glass functionalities.

